title: Pay our new Community Manager 300 SNAFU per week
body:
# We would like to pay Reem 300 SNAFU per week, taken from the DAO funds, for his services as Community Manager.

We opened a thread on our forum to discuss it and there was no contrary feedback, so we are now putting this to vote.
You can find the discussion [here]( https://forum.nftsnafu.org/t/pay-reem-300-snafu-per-week-for-the-work-as-community-manager/31).

-----

### Do you agree to pay Reem 300 SNAFU per week using the DAO funds?
author: 0x52eB606f94091A2BA4f985D98C62880a9BA591B6
